{
  "stem": "12564.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell by who you left the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we'll let you go free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know that you're hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't eat already a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He gave me herring to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was silly enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With a small piece of bread, very salty herring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, you can go back to your room already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went to the room back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no water, anymore, there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And 24 hours, nobody showed up to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I thought, I'll burn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after this, they called me in again for investigation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The guy sits and sips water and ask questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did not reveal for one reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The family was a friend with three little kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I will not put a man in jail if I know that he'll die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what-- what you do to get out of this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I went back to the cell-- cell-- and I was sitting in [? solitary ?] confinement, alone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This already, four months, took at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the end of the four months-- after the herring episode, for this, a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I must find a way to get out of this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did it in time from the war, somehow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I should find a way here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing with what to write, I had a comb for the hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I ripped-- pulled out a tooth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I wrote down a testament on the wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I figured out how to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Slowly, from the towers, I was pulling out threads.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I made a rope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The heating pipe was going with the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At 7:00 in the morning, the guard was changing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When the guard changed, one took over from the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
